## **4. Workflow Engine - Process Flow**  
### **4.1 Parsing & Validation**  
```mermaid  
graph TD  
    A[Workflow JSON] --> B[Syntax Validator]  
    B --> C[Schema Validator]  
    C --> D[Dependency Resolver]  
    D --> E[DAG Optimizer]  
```
**Validation Rules**:  
```json  
{  
  "required": ["nodes", "edges"],  
  "properties": {  
    "nodes": {  
      "items": {  
        "required": ["id", "type"]  
      }  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

